data.description: 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch style townhome in the highly desirable Indigo Ridge area! This home features a bright and open floor plan, large kitchen with ample cabinets and breakfast bar, dining area with walk-out access to the rear deck and spacious living area with gas fireplace. Don’t forget about the garden level basement which boasts a family room, bathroom and an office! All this and more centrally located in a quiet, gated community, close to Memorial Park, Pete Field, military installations, Colorado Springs Airport, and Valley Hi Golf Course.
